Q: Where you should write the vagrantfile?
If we are working on a java project, the project directory structure looks like-
project
-src
--main
---java
---resources
---webapp
-----web-INF
-----web.xml
-POM.xml
-Vagrant configration file


How to create vagrant file?
Vagrant.configure(2) do | config |
end

Create a first vm using vagrant?

Vagrant.configure(2) do | config |
config.vm.box="hashicorp/precise64"
end




